sub_title: Change execution professional ING N.V. Nederland
summary:
A highly capable result oriented project manager with an experience in project and portfolio management, project implementation and financial analysis, with proven leadership and strategy skills. I am a natural communicator with accurate and analytical thinking that can always remain calm under pressure. I have a proven track record of successful management of simultaneous projects with demonstrated experience working within a dynamic environment of change.
Formerly working in Directorate for project implementation of European structural and investment funds in the fields of: 
- Technology and innovation 
- Retail
- Information and communications technology 
- Small and medium - sized enterprises 
- E-commerce 
- Business intelligence systems 
(list is not exhaustive).
I am Multilingual with proficiency in English, German, Croatian and Slovenian. 
Strong professional with a Masters Degree focused in Business & Management.
PSM I certificate holder.
